  "keyFeatures": [
    "LangSmith tracing and observability for AI agents",
    "Customer support agent (Emma) with progressive improvements",
    "Code-based, LLM-as-judge, and pairwise evaluation methods",
    "SQLite database integration for product inventory",
    "RAG-based knowledge base search with embeddings",
    "Production-ready trace upload and online evaluation",
    "Parallel Python and TypeScript implementations"
